    "description": {
      "content": "The Squarespace Inventory API enables reading and adjusting stock information for product variants on a Squarespace merchant site. Developers can retrieve current inventory levels and apply incremental adjustments to stock quantities. This API is useful for integrating Squarespace with warehouse management systems, point-of-sale systems, or multi-channel inventory management platforms. Inventory adjustments can be applied in bulk across multiple product variants.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Squarespace Developer Support",
